    "description": "Lightweight software agent deployed on managed endpoints that continuously collects operational telemetry including system performance metrics, resource utilization, process state, event log data, service health, hardware sensor readings, and application availability indicators. Transmits collected data to centralized monitoring platforms for aggregation, threshold alerting, trend analysis, and capacity planning. May operate in conjunction with security telemetry pipelines and SIEM integrations.",
